																										<p><a href="/news/world/africa/ethiopia-braced-for-more-violence-over-musician-s-killing-1.4295309" class="gtm-event" data-evt-category="Section element" data-evt-action="/news/world/africa/ethiopia-braced-for-more-violence-over-musician-s-killing-1.4295309 on /news/world/africa" data-evt-label="Position 3 of 100">Scores of people dead in clashes following Haacaaluu Hundeessaa&rsquo;s death on Monday</a></p>
